fn.description:
Decides whether to use `test` or `it`.

Examples of **incorrect** code for `{ "fn": "test" }`:
```javascript
it('foo');
it.only('foo');
```

Examples of **correct** code for `{ "fn": "test" }`:
```javascript
test('foo');
test.only('foo');
```

Examples of **incorrect** code for `{ "fn": "it" }`:
```javascript
test('foo');
test.only('foo');
```

Examples of **correct** code for `{ "fn": "it" }`:
```javascript
it('foo');
it.only('foo');
```

